</P>
<P>
 A First Look Pictures release. Producer-director Adolfo Aristarain. Executive 
producer Isidro Miguel. Screenplay by Aristarain with Alberto Lecchi; from a 
story by Aristarain and Kathy Saavedra. Cinematographer Ricardo De Angelis. 
Editor Eduardo Lopez. Costumes Saavedra. Art director Abel Facello. In Spanish 
with English subtitles. Running time: 2 hous, 4 minutes. 
</P>
<P>
