 Police are asking the public to help identify a dead woman whose body was 
found on fire near the Foothill Freeway in Tujunga, LAPD Foothill Division 
Detective Marv Whiting said. 
</P>
<P>
 The woman, believed to be in her mid-20s, was discovered by passersby in the 
