according to Homicide Detective Keith Honore of Foothill Division.Police 
believe she was dead at the time she was set afire, Whiting said. 
</P>
<P>
 She was either Latina or Caucasian, 5-foot-6 and 135 pounds, and had black 
hair and brown eyes. 
</P>
<P>
 Although the incident is under investigation as a homicide, the coroner's 
office has not determined whether the woman was slain, Whiting said. 
</P>
