BRIEFCASE: REAL ESTATE; PROPERTY AUCTIONS REMAIN A POPULAR MARKETING TOOL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 After gaining popularity during the real estate downturn, property auctions in 
Orange County continue to be an attractive selling tool during the recovery, 
brokers say. 
</P>
<P>
 SperryVan Ness, a Newport Beach real estate brokerage, announced Tuesday that 
it has combined forces with an Alabama auction company to sell retail, 
industrial, apartment and commercial properties, as well as undeveloped land. 
</P>
