<TEXT>
<P>
 Boxing -- Yugoslavian boxer Anton Josipovic and referee Gligorije Novicic were 
misidentified in the Aug. 10 edition. Also, Josipovic, not New Zealand's Kevin 
Barry, won the light-heavyweight gold medal in the 1984 Olympics. Barry won the 
silver. 
</P>
