<TEXT>
<P>
 Federal judge -- A headline in Tuesday's editions incorrectly identified A. 
Andrew Hauk as a federal circuit judge.In fact, Hauk is a District Court judge, 
assigned to the Central District of California. The story also incorrectly 
referred to the code that allows complaints to be filed against a federal 
judge. Such complaints are governed by the U.S. Code. 
</P>
</TEXT>
