<TEXT>
<P>
 Cancer Research -- UC Irvine researchers are recruiting children with cancer 
from all ethnic groups, including Native Americans, for enrollment in clinical 
testing. In a story Tuesday, UCI officials mentioned only Latinos, Asians and 
African Americans. Potential participants can call Dr. Paul Zeltzer at (714) 
456-8411. 
</P>
